        "author_association": "MEMBER",
        "body": "The owner is not necessarily the direct parent, it can be further up in the tree. Usually the owner is the root of the scene saved to the disk, because the editor sets that automatically.\r\n\r\nNote that if you are relying on the owner, for nodes you instance you have to set the owner manually, because it's not set by default.",
